{"tid":610170,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"愛情到底係命運，定係選擇？","createTime":"2018-03-29T16:24:16.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-31T05:58:31.000Z","uid":31340,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"34f11917c4af626b4b2df097510173d961a26ebf","tid":610170,"uid":31340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-29T16:24:16.000Z","msg":"有時候我地會遇到一個一見到就覺得係命中注定既人，<br />\n有時候我地會遇到一個一見到冇諗過會係變成情侶既人（姐係純粹係佢追你你後尾受左）。<br />\n如果你係相信命運既，但你既愛情係後者既情況下發生，你係咪一定會放棄？<br />\n另外，如果雙方都覺得係命中注定，當然係完美，但如果有一方唔覺得係命中注定但仍然肯行落去，咁係咪代表呢段愛情係有瑕疵？"},{"pid":"e9594c66351d988a4fb138b779ae01258768cb34","tid":610170,"uid":39215,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-29T16:26:57.000Z","msg":"緣聚緣散 皆有定數"},{"pid":"490949e86530b327af0ddad98d4d8dbdb4e8d6d5","tid":610170,"uid":133042,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-29T18:18:03.000Z","msg":"我諗起有句說話我覺得講得好啱, &quot; we fall in love by chance, but we stay in love by choice&quot;"},{"pid":"44bca23ff563080d59320509c92241fd90a82187","tid":610170,"uid":106326,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-29T18:41:52.000Z","msg":"我很快就適應了這種生活，開始懂得逢場作戲，雖然多半是露水情緣，不過，沒關係啦，哪來那麼多的一生一世？"},{"pid":"85da4e70fc1016ac51e829708cefc8556840ef26","tid":610170,"uid":161537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-29T19:29:29.000Z","msg":"你係有錢仔或靚女咪係選擇<br />\n其他都係命運多"},{"pid":"49da6792983d7a16b494dc8fab15beabadbfe829","tid":610170,"uid":36402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-29T19:34:46.000Z","msg":"沒有命運的巧合和選擇錯了都不會得到你想要的愛情"},{"pid":"f0aecf548ba5c438d8bf0dc4b1b6bcb427acbbae","tid":610170,"uid":111625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-30T12:08:19.000Z","msg":"一切都是注定的"},{"pid":"b84422e6222452f670075f279197afe9612ef170","tid":610170,"uid":143307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-30T12:09:33.000Z","msg":"緣在天定 份靠人為"},{"pid":"01c29567a614105be5a94887c28ba4a5ceddcd9c","tid":610170,"uid":143206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-30T12:12:17.000Z","msg":"both"},{"pid":"13b508f12ea4fede24505aa30aa85f4c73668f58","tid":610170,"uid":120418,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-30T12:19:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>緣在天定 份靠人為</blockquote><br />\nagree<br />\n緣係天賜，份係靠自己維繫"},{"pid":"4f2d6eac468b38324f142e9118ffcf55514fd4d7","tid":610170,"uid":73349,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-30T12:22:02.000Z","msg":"無論有無結果，好定壞，我都信係命運"},{"pid":"1b8024b4e94ab93b5f3bc97ece7ea05d44b8ef69","tid":610170,"uid":31340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T05:52:58.000Z","msg":"相愛到係命運，行到落去係選擇。<br />\n假如最後有一方選擇唔行落去，而另一方卻選擇繼續追隨，最後都係失敗，咁對被遺棄嗰個黎講，<br />\n一齊唔到最終都好似命運？<br />\n只有兩方都選擇大家時先係選擇？定係都係命運。<br />\n好迷茫。"},{"pid":"7e492a33eb1d760efa282c6927852255625d55d1","tid":610170,"uid":92230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T05:58:31.000Z","msg":"你既選擇空間係命運決定"}]}